---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import MyButton from '../components/button.jsx';
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 px-6 py-10">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-8">
      
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sky-700">
          Goals
        </p>
        <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 md:text-6xl">
          Set sleep improvement goals
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-600">
          Create your own goals and get suggestions based on the daily habits that may affect your deep sleep.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr]">
        
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:p-8">
          <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Create your own goal</h2>

          <form class="grid gap-6">
            <div>
              <label class="mb-2 block font-semibold text-slate-800">Goal title</label>
              <input
                type="text"
                placeholder="e.g. No caffeine after 3 PM"
                class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-3 outline-none transition focus:border-sky-500"
              />
            </div>

            <div>
              <label class="mb-2 block font-semibold text-slate-800">Why do you want this goal?</label>
              <textarea
                rows="4"
                placeholder="e.g. I think late coffee is reducing my deep sleep."
                class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-3 outline-none transition focus:border-sky-500"
              ></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
              <div>
                <label class="mb-2 block font-semibold text-slate-800">Category</label>
                <select class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-3 outline-none transition focus:border-sky-500">
                  <option value="">Select category</option>
                  <option value="caffeine">Caffeine</option>
                  <option value="screen-time">Screen time</option>
                  <option value="phone-use">Phone use</option>
                  <option value="activity">Physical activity</option>
                  <option value="sleep">Sleep routine</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <div>
                <label class="mb-2 block font-semibold text-slate-800">Target duration</label>
                <select class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-3 outline-none transition focus:border-sky-500">
                  <option value="">Select duration</option>
                  <option value="3days">3 days</option>
                  <option value="1week">1 week</option>
                  <option value="2weeks">2 weeks</option>
                  <option value="1month">1 month</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label class="mb-2 block font-semibold text-slate-800">Reminder preference</label>
              <select class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-3 outline-none transition focus:border-sky-500">
                <option value="">Select reminder type</option>
                <option value="none">No reminder</option>
                <option value="daily">Daily reminder</option>
                <option value="habit-risk">Only when risky habit is detected</option>
                <option value="evening">Evening reminder</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-2">
              <MyButton name="Save Goal" />
              <a href="/dashboard">
                <MyButton name="Back to Dashboard" />
              </a>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Suggested goals</h2>
            <p class="mb-5 text-slate-600">
              Suggestions can adapt to patterns detected in the user’s daily entries.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-sky-50 p-4">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-sky-700">Caffeine pattern</p>
                <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Avoid caffeine after 3 PM</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">
                  Useful if late caffeine appears on days with reduced deep sleep.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 p-4">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700">Activity pattern</p>
                <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Reach 8,000 steps daily</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">
                  Useful if low-activity days seem related to worse sleep quality.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-violet-50 p-4">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-violet-700">Screen routine</p>
                <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Reduce screen time in the evening</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">
                  Useful if high screen time or late phone use appears before poor sleep nights.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-amber-50 p-4">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-amber-700">Sleep consistency</p>
                <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Keep a more regular bedtime</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">
                  Useful if irregular routines are linked with shorter or lower-quality sleep.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-900 p-6 text-white shadow-sm">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">How suggestions work</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-300">
              The system compares daily habits such as caffeine after 3 PM, steps, screen time,
              and last phone use time with sleep outcomes to propose useful goals for behavior change.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
